				"img": "icons/magic/perception/orb-crystal-ball-scrying.webp",
				"description": "<p>Your offering and magic put you in contact with the higher power you serve or its representatives.</p><p>You ask a single question about something that will (or could) happen in the next 7 days. The Narrator offers a truthful reply, which may be cryptic or even nonverbal as appropriate to the being in question.</p><p>The reply does not account for possible circumstances that could change the outcome, such as making additional precautions.</p><p>When you cast this spell again before finishing a long rest, the chance of getting a random reading from the above options increases. The Narrator makes the following roll in secret: second casting&mdash;25%, third casting&mdash;50%, fourth casting&mdash;75%, fifth casting&mdash;100%.</p>",
